I ran away when I was 16.

523
00:45:22.846 --> 00:45:25.474
As soon as I knew my
brother wasn't coming back.

524
00:45:26.391 --> 00:45:29.394
You started an underground
fight ring in Macau

525
00:45:30.020 --> 00:45:31.772
when you were 16 years old?

526
00:45:33.231 --> 00:45:36.193
If my dad won't let
me into his empire.

527
00:45:36.276 --> 00:45:37.736
I'm gonna build my own.

528
00:45:39.029 --> 00:45:40.363
Hell yeah.

529
00:46:06.723 --> 00:46:07.724
Shang-Chi.

530
00:46:10.268 --> 00:46:12.145
That's enough.

531
00:46:18.443 --> 00:46:20.904
Have you been
practicing your English?

532
00:46:23.073 --> 00:46:24.199
Yes.

533
00:46:26.201 --> 00:46:29.871
You have to strengthen your
mind along with your body.

534
00:46:36.253 --> 00:46:39.798
If you want them to
be yours one day.

535
00:46:39.965 --> 00:46:43.885
you have to show me you're
strong enough to carry them.

536
00:47:01.486 --> 00:47:02.988
How did you find me?

537
00:47:03.780 --> 00:47:06.032
I always know where
my children are.

538
00:47:06.992 --> 00:47:08.827
I gave you 10 years
to live your life.

539
00:47:08.910 --> 00:47:10.203
and where did it get you?

540
00:47:13.456 --> 00:47:17.294
Now it's time for you to
take your place by my side.

541
00:47:18.295 --> 00:47:20.630
That's not gonna happen.

542
00:47:24.134 --> 00:47:25.760
American girl.

543
00:47:25.927 --> 00:47:27.053
Her name is Katy.

544
00:47:28.346 --> 00:47:30.015
What is your Chinese name?

545
00:47:34.019 --> 00:47:35.312
Ruiwen.

546
00:47:36.354 --> 00:47:38.523
Names are sacred. Ruiwen.

547
00:47:38.690 --> 00:47:40.692
They connect us not
only to ourselves.

548
00:47:40.775 --> 00:47:42.569
but to everyone who came before.

549
00:47:44.029 --> 00:47:45.697
A funny story.

550
00:47:45.864 --> 00:47:48.325
Some years ago. a
terrorist from America

551
00:47:48.408 --> 00:47:49.826
needed a boogeyman

552
00:47:49.993 --> 00:47:52.621
to bring your
country to its knees.

553
00:47:52.787 --> 00:47:55.457
So. he appropriated
The Ten Rings.

554
00:47:55.540 --> 00:47:56.541
My Ten Rings.

555
00:47:56.625 --> 00:47:59.127
But because he didn't
know my actual name.

556
00:47:59.210 --> 00:48:00.587
he invented a new one.

557
00:48:01.212 --> 00:48:03.173
Do you know the name he chose?

558
00:48:05.008 --> 00:48:06.551
The Mandarin.

559
00:48:06.718 --> 00:48:09.679
He gave his figurehead the
name of a chicken dish.

560
00:48:10.096 --> 00:48:11.514
And it worked.

561
00:48:11.681 --> 00:48:13.475
America was terrified.

562
00:48:14.351 --> 00:48:15.936
Of an orange.

563
00:48:17.729 --> 00:48:19.022
The truth is.

564
00:48:19.189 --> 00:48:22.067
I've had many names
throughout my life.

565
00:48:22.776 --> 00:48:25.195
The Warrior King. Master Khan.

566
00:48:25.278 --> 00:48:27.405
the most dangerous man on Earth.

567
00:48:27.739 --> 00:48:31.785
For years. I thought that
was all I was meant to be.

568
00:48:34.621 --> 00:48:37.499
But when I met their mother.

569
00:48:38.249 --> 00:48:40.043
everything changed.

570
00:48:54.265 --> 00:48:57.894
<i>She showed me a part of myself
I didn't know was there.</i>

571
00:49:00.647 --> 00:49:03.525
<i>It was like I was seeing the
world for the first time.</i>

572
00:49:13.702 --> 00:49:17.247
<i>She gave up everything
so we could be together.</i>

573
00:49:20.500 --> 00:49:22.168
<i>And so did I.</i>

574
00:49:37.225 --> 00:49:38.893
You know who's in there?

575
00:49:39.060 --> 00:49:40.895
Say. "Hello. little sister!"

576
00:49:47.360 --> 00:49:48.820
<i>After
all those years.</i>

577
00:49:48.903 --> 00:49:50.488
<i>I finally found something</i>

578
00:49:50.655 --> 00:49:52.824
<i>worth growing old for.</i>

579
00:49:58.288 --> 00:50:00.665
My real name is Wenwu.

580
00:50:01.499 --> 00:50:04.085
She was the only one
who called me that.

581
00:50:05.754 --> 00:50:07.547
And when she died...

582
00:50:10.759 --> 00:50:13.094
I was lost for many years.

583
00:50:15.805 --> 00:50:17.807
But I'm not lost anymore.

584
00:50:22.187 --> 00:50:23.646
When you children ran away.

585
00:50:23.813 --> 00:50:26.357
I was so desperate to
connect with your mother.

586
00:50:26.524 --> 00:50:29.736
I threw myself back into
the studies of her village.

587
00:50:30.320 --> 00:50:32.113
The legendary Ta Lo.

588
00:50:33.323 --> 00:50:34.491
I wasn't able

589
00:50:34.574 --> 00:50:36.826
to find the secret path
to the village entrance.

590
00:50:36.993 --> 00:50:40.538
but I did find what
they are hiding.

591
00:50:41.081 --> 00:50:43.625
There's a gate deep
in their mountains.

592
00:50:44.292 --> 00:50:46.961
Your mother is
waiting for us there.

593
00:50:49.923 --> 00:50:51.549
I know this is a lot.

594
00:50:51.758 --> 00:50:55.595
I might not have believed it
if she didn't tell me herself.

595
00:50:56.429 --> 00:50:58.056
What are you talking about?

596
00:50:58.556 --> 00:51:00.642
I was sitting right
here in this seat.

597
00:51:01.059 --> 00:51:03.103
deep in my research...

598
00:51:04.312 --> 00:51:06.189
and she spoke to me.

599
00:51:06.981 --> 00:51:09.734
It was like she was
standing in this room.

600
00:51:09.901 --> 00:51:12.737
I could feel her
breath on my cheek

601
00:51:12.821 --> 00:51:14.781
and her hand on my back.

602
00:51:16.324 --> 00:51:18.576
She told me she needs my help.

603
00:51:20.328 --> 00:51:21.538
To do what?

604
00:51:22.330 --> 00:51:24.707
To save her from her people.

605
00:51:27.877 --> 00:51:29.712
After we fell in love.

606
00:51:29.796 --> 00:51:32.507
your mother wanted
us to live in Ta Lo.

607
00:51:32.674 --> 00:51:34.676
She asked permission
from the elders.

608
00:51:34.759 --> 00:51:35.927
and they refused.

609
00:51:36.094 --> 00:51:38.304
They said I wasn't worthy.

610
00:51:40.098 --> 00:51:41.432
She would still be with us.

611
00:51:41.516 --> 00:51:44.144
We would all be
living there together.

612
00:51:44.936 --> 00:51:46.646
Ta Lo did this to us.

613
00:51:48.439 --> 00:51:51.067
They locked her behind
that gate to punish her.

614
00:51:55.488 --> 00:51:56.739
Don't you see?

615
00:51:57.699 --> 00:51:59.784
She's leaving clues for us.

616
00:51:59.951 --> 00:52:01.411
She wants us to find her

617
00:52:01.578 --> 00:52:04.330
and bring her home. so
we can be a family again.

618
00:52:05.206 --> 00:52:07.876
Dad. Mom's gone.

619
00:52:09.210 --> 00:52:11.171
She's not talking to
you from behind a gate.

620
00:52:11.254 --> 00:52:13.548
and she's not leaving
any clues for us.

621
00:52:18.887 --> 00:52:21.055
Then what are these?

622
00:53:07.393 --> 00:53:11.064
The passage to Ta Lo is
guarded by a moving maze.

623
00:53:12.106 --> 00:53:15.235
But there's a direct
path through the forest

624
00:53:15.318 --> 00:53:17.403
that only opens once a year

625
00:53:17.570 --> 00:53:19.489
on Qingming Jie.

626
00:53:20.448 --> 00:53:22.992
To get through. you
need to know the route

627
00:53:23.076 --> 00:53:25.453
and the exact time it opens.

628
00:53:29.874 --> 00:53:31.501
Now I know both.

629
00:53:43.263 --> 00:53:45.306
Three days from now.

630
00:53:45.473 --> 00:53:47.850
we will rescue my
wife from her prison

631
00:53:47.934 --> 00:53:49.143
and bring her home.

632
00:53:55.817 --> 00:53:57.485
This is why you're here.

633
00:53:58.403 --> 00:53:59.988
To help me bring her back to us.

634
00:54:00.571 --> 00:54:02.865
And what happens if they
don't let you open the gate?

635
00:54:04.492 --> 00:54:07.912
We'll burn the
village to the ground.

636
00:54:09.956 --> 00:54:10.957
What?

637
00:54:13.668 --> 00:54:15.962
You can't just march
into our mom's village

638
00:54:16.045 --> 00:54:17.463
with this bullshit.

639
00:54:17.880 --> 00:54:19.520
I mean. do you have
any idea how insane...

640
00:54:24.679 --> 00:54:25.680
Hey!

641
00:54:28.558 --> 00:54:31.102
Where are you taking me?

642
00:54:32.478 --> 00:54:34.772
When will you stop pretending?

643
00:54:37.483 --> 00:54:38.651
Lock them up.

644
00:54:58.296 --> 00:55:01.466
It's okay. my dear.

645
00:55:08.389 --> 00:55:12.560
We're all going to
be together soon.

646
00:55:21.152 --> 00:55:25.948
So. um.
pretty confused right now.

647
00:55:26.115 --> 00:55:29.660
because. uh. initially I
thought your dad should

648
00:55:29.869 --> 00:55:31.788
definitely see a therapist
for his delusions.

649
00:55:31.996 --> 00:55:35.583
but then that dragon
vomited a magical water map.

650
00:55:36.334 --> 00:55:38.711
and now I have no
idea what's real.

651
00:55:41.130 --> 00:55:43.466
Is what he said about
your mom's village true?

652
00:55:47.178 --> 00:55:48.655
She used to tell us
stories about Ta Lo

653
00:55:48.679 --> 00:55:49.680
when we were kids.

654
00:55:50.723 --> 00:55:54.936
A village in another dimension
full of magical creatures.

655
00:55:55.019 --> 00:55:57.021
I thought it was
just a fairy tale.

656
00:55:58.981 --> 00:56:00.817
What if Dad's right?

657
00:56:02.610 --> 00:56:04.004
About Mom being
locked behind a gate

658
00:56:04.028 --> 00:56:05.988
by her own people?

659
00:56:06.155 --> 00:56:08.408
Crazier things have
turned out to be true.

660
00:56:09.617 --> 00:56:11.786
Look. I don't know what
the hell is going on.

661
00:56:11.953 --> 00:56:14.372
but if we don't find a way
to get to Ta Lo before him.

662
00:56:14.539 --> 00:56:16.958
he's gonna destroy everything
that's left of our family.

663
00:56:19.252 --> 00:56:22.130
This family was destroyed
a long time ago.

664
00:56:26.426 --> 00:56:28.094
The hell was that?

665
00:56:28.177 --> 00:56:30.346
Oh.

666
00:56:30.430 --> 00:56:32.682
You're going
toward that noise?

667
00:56:52.201 --> 00:56:55.496
"Wake Duncan with thy knocking.

668
00:56:55.663 --> 00:56:58.624
"Oh. I would'st though could'st.

669
00:56:58.791 --> 00:57:00.334
"My deed 'twere best not..."

670
00:57:03.337 --> 00:57:05.298
Oh. hello. loves.

671
00:57:06.424 --> 00:57:07.884
What year is it?

672
00:57:09.385 --> 00:57:10.761
Who are you?

673
00:57:10.928 --> 00:57:13.055
Trevor? Slattery?

674
00:57:13.222 --> 00:57:15.641
The actor from Liverpool?

675
00:57:16.559 --> 00:57:17.560
Wait.

676
00:57:17.727 --> 00:57:19.270
Are you the governor's kids?

677
00:57:19.937 --> 00:57:21.564
I've been preparing a monologue

678
00:57:21.647 --> 00:57:23.316
for your homecoming dinner.

679
00:57:23.483 --> 00:57:25.359
Oh. Where's she going?

680
00:57:25.526 --> 00:57:26.694
Why are you down here?

681
00:57:26.861 --> 00:57:28.821
Well. some time ago.

682
00:57:28.905 --> 00:57:30.448
I was offered the
role of a terrorist.

683
00:57:30.656 --> 00:57:32.909
I know. facile. trite.
I couldn't agree more.

684
00:57:33.075 --> 00:57:34.994
But times were lean.
you know what I mean?

685
00:57:35.161 --> 00:57:37.914
Anyway. the producer told
me he worked for the BBC.

686
00:57:38.080 --> 00:57:39.540
But. ironic twist.

687
00:57:39.624 --> 00:57:42.210
it turns out he. in
fact. was a terrorist.

688
00:57:42.376 --> 00:57:43.936
and I wasn't playing
a character at all.

689
00:57:44.045 --> 00:57:45.338
but what I now recognize to be

690
00:57:45.421 --> 00:57:47.381
a rather unflattering
portrait of your father.

691
00:57:47.798 --> 00:57:49.550
We all got our just deserts.

692
00:57:49.717 --> 00:57:51.594
The producer got
blown up by Iron Man.

693
00:57:51.677 --> 00:57:53.346
and I served time
in federal prison.

694
00:57:53.513 --> 00:57:56.349
which turned out to be
the best thing for me.

695
00:57:56.432 --> 00:57:58.851
I got clean. I
rediscovered my passion.

696
00:57:59.018 --> 00:58:01.604
- Then my dad broke you out?
- Exactly.

697
00:58:01.771 --> 00:58:03.856
- To kill you.
- Exactly.

698
00:58:04.607 --> 00:58:06.943
But just as his men

699
00:58:07.026 --> 00:58:09.654
were tying me up
for my execution.

700
00:58:09.820 --> 00:58:11.697
I launched into a
performance of my Macbeth.

701
00:58:11.781 --> 00:58:13.407
"Whence is that
knocking? Wake Duncan

702
00:58:13.491 --> 00:58:15.052
"with thy knocking. I
would'st though could'st..."

703
00:58:15.076 --> 00:58:16.316
They couldn't get enough of it.

704
00:58:16.410 --> 00:58:18.829
I've been doing weekly gigs
for the lads ever since.

705
00:58:18.996 --> 00:58:20.873
So you're like his jester?

706
00:58:21.040 --> 00:58:22.720
I can give you a quick
preview if you like.

707
00:58:22.792 --> 00:58:24.043
"Nuncle. nuncle. nuncle..."

708
00:58:24.210 --> 00:58:26.504
Uh. thank you. Trevor.
I think we're okay.

709
00:58:26.712 --> 00:58:28.607
Right now. we really just
need to find a way to...

710
00:58:28.631 --> 00:58:30.071
What the hell?

711
00:58:30.132 --> 00:58:31.259
What the... Oh!

712
00:58:31.342 --> 00:58:32.385
- Whoa!
- What is that?

713
00:58:34.095 --> 00:58:35.096
What's what?

714
00:58:35.263 --> 00:58:37.056
- That! What is that?
- That! That! That!

715
00:58:39.392 --> 00:58:40.726
You can see Morris?

716
00:58:40.893 --> 00:58:41.894
Morris?

717
00:58:41.978 --> 00:58:44.647
Oh. Morris!

718
00:58:44.814 --> 00:58:47.149
They can see you! You're real!

719
00:58:47.316 --> 00:58:50.361
All this time I thought
I was hallucinating him.

720
00:58:50.528 --> 00:58:52.029
Oh. this is such fab news.

721
00:58:53.114 --> 00:58:54.115
Where's his face?

722
00:58:55.741 --> 00:58:57.410
He's a bit sensitive about that.

723
00:58:58.536 --> 00:59:00.246
Oh. Really?

724
00:59:01.872 --> 00:59:03.499
Morris says he
knows who you are.

725
00:59:04.208 --> 00:59:05.543
It talks... It talks to you?

726
00:59:05.626 --> 00:59:07.169
If he
didn't talk to me.

727
00:59:07.253 --> 00:59:09.088
I'd have gone mad yonks ago.

728
00:59:10.464 --> 00:59:11.841
How
would he know me?

729
00:59:12.008 --> 00:59:14.844
He says he grew up with
your mum. In Ta Lo.

730
00:59:15.720 --> 00:59:18.806
Apparently. your father picked
him up in some magic forest

731
00:59:18.973 --> 00:59:21.684
on one of his expeditions
to find the entrance.

732
00:59:25.354 --> 00:59:26.939
He wants you to take him home.

733
00:59:29.525 --> 00:59:31.569
Believe me. buddy. I
would if I knew how.

734
00:59:32.278 --> 00:59:33.279
According to my dad.

735
00:59:33.362 --> 00:59:35.114
the path there only
opens once a year.

736
00:59:38.618 --> 00:59:40.786
Oh.

737
00:59:41.996 --> 00:59:44.582
Morris says he can guide
you there right now.

738
00:59:44.749 --> 00:59:45.958
You can get through the maze

739
00:59:46.042 --> 00:59:47.627
without waiting for
the path to open.

740
00:59:47.793 --> 00:59:49.795
But. and it's a big "but."

741
00:59:49.962 --> 00:59:52.006
it's very dangerous.

742
00:59:52.173 --> 00:59:53.174
How dangerous?

743
00:59:53.341 --> 00:59:55.259
No one's ever made it out alive.

744
00:59:55.426 --> 00:59:58.220
But Morris is 90% confident

745
00:59:58.387 --> 01:00:00.139
he can guide us through safely.

746
01:00:00.222 --> 01:00:01.766
Oh.

747
01:00:01.849 --> 01:00:03.351
19%.

748
01:00:05.853 --> 01:00:08.356
Look. I've done dumber
things with worse odds.

749
01:00:08.522 --> 01:00:10.232
But even if that
chicken-pig is right...

750
01:00:11.400 --> 01:00:12.461
we're still locked in your...

751
01:00:18.616 --> 01:00:19.742
Whew!

752
01:00:22.703 --> 01:00:23.996
How did you...

753
01:00:24.163 --> 01:00:26.582
Dad has a tunnel system
under the whole compound.

754
01:00:26.749 --> 01:00:28.501
That's how I escaped last time.

755
01:00:28.668 --> 01:00:29.669
Oh.

756
01:00:29.752 --> 01:00:31.796
This will take us
straight to the garage.

757
01:00:43.516 --> 01:00:45.351
Oh. my God.

758
01:00:45.518 --> 01:00:47.019
I kinda like this guy.

759
01:00:47.186 --> 01:00:49.146
Just head up that ramp and
through the front gate.

760
01:00:49.188 --> 01:00:50.314
Should be a straight shot.

761
01:00:50.398 --> 01:00:52.108
Figure we got about
30 seconds until he...

762
01:00:52.274 --> 01:00:53.275
Do you mind?

763
01:00:53.442 --> 01:00:55.403
I get sick in the
back. Carsick.

764
01:00:58.614 --> 01:00:59.782
That's my car!

765
01:01:05.371 --> 01:01:06.372
God damn it.

766
01:01:06.539 --> 01:01:07.665
Hold on.

767
01:01:09.166 --> 01:01:10.209
Is there another exit?

768
01:01:10.292 --> 01:01:11.544
The other end of the garage.

769
01:01:11.711 --> 01:01:13.212
But we need a
fingerprint to open it.

770
01:01:20.010 --> 01:01:21.345
Incoming!

771
01:01:22.722 --> 01:01:23.848
Shit!

772
01:01:45.828 --> 01:01:47.204
What's
happening back there?

773
01:01:48.539 --> 01:01:49.623
Doing my best.

774
01:01:49.749 --> 01:01:51.601
<i>Scan hand
print for gate access.</i>

775
01:01:51.625 --> 01:01:53.919
- Hurry up!
- I'm trying!

776
01:01:56.255 --> 01:01:57.399
<i>Scan hand print for gate access.</i>

777
01:01:57.423 --> 01:01:58.424
Shaun!

778
01:01:59.592 --> 01:02:01.177
<i>Access approved.</i>

779
01:02:19.904 --> 01:02:22.323
They will come back
once I bring her home.

780
01:02:24.158 --> 01:02:25.910
Prepare the men for war.

781
01:02:26.911 --> 01:02:27.953
Yes. sir.

782
01:02:33.000 --> 01:02:36.462
The first time I
witnessed pure artistry.

783
01:02:36.837 --> 01:02:40.591
1968. <i>Planet of the Apes.</i>

784
01:02:40.758 --> 01:02:42.760
I was sitting in the
cinema next to my mum.

785
01:02:42.843 --> 01:02:44.303
watching mastery

786
01:02:44.470 --> 01:02:46.347
unfold before my very eyes.

787
01:02:46.514 --> 01:02:48.641
After the film. I asked her.

788
01:02:48.808 --> 01:02:51.227
"How did they get those
monkeys to do those things?"

789
01:02:51.393 --> 01:02:54.188
And she patted me on
the head and she said.

790
01:02:54.355 --> 01:02:57.233
"It's not real. pet.
It's just acting."

791
01:02:57.399 --> 01:02:59.109
That's when I knew.

792
01:03:00.194 --> 01:03:01.612
If they can teach those monkeys

793
01:03:01.695 --> 01:03:03.614
to act that brilliantly.

794
01:03:04.281 --> 01:03:07.535
just imagine what I
could bring to the world.

795
01:03:08.118 --> 01:03:09.245
So you became an actor

796
01:03:09.411 --> 01:03:11.330
because you thought the
monkeys were actually...

797
01:03:11.497 --> 01:03:14.166
Riding horses? I did. Yes.

798
01:03:14.333 --> 01:03:15.918
When. in fact.

799
01:03:16.001 --> 01:03:19.088
they were simply acting as
if they were riding horses.

800
01:03:19.255 --> 01:03:21.465
I still can't get my head
round it. to be honest.

801
01:03:22.508 --> 01:03:24.301
Good for you. dude.

802
01:03:24.844 --> 01:03:28.305
You found your passion
and went for it.

803
01:03:28.472 --> 01:03:29.557
and eventually used it

804
01:03:29.640 --> 01:03:31.684
to cripple the US
government. but whatever.

805
01:03:31.851 --> 01:03:33.811
Yeah.
No. yeah. thanks.

806
01:03:33.894 --> 01:03:35.896
Um. this is really cool and all.

807
01:03:35.980 --> 01:03:37.439
but how long do we
have to sit here?

808
01:03:37.606 --> 01:03:39.066
Morris is very clear.

809
01:03:39.650 --> 01:03:41.527
The way through is
all about timing.

810
01:03:42.027 --> 01:03:43.737
Okay. but how long
are we talking?

811
01:03:43.904 --> 01:03:45.614
Like. hours? Days?

812
01:03:45.781 --> 01:03:48.409
Friends. I am but
a transitory vessel

813
01:03:48.492 --> 01:03:49.932
for the infinite
wisdom of a creature

814
01:03:50.077 --> 01:03:52.329
far more advanced than
we'll ever truly understand.

815
01:03:52.955 --> 01:03:54.582
What he sees. what he feels

816
01:03:54.665 --> 01:03:56.375
of this vast. unknown universe

817
01:03:56.542 --> 01:03:58.460
is beyond anything our
simple brains can...

818
01:03:58.544 --> 01:03:59.962
Oh. You can go.

819
01:04:00.379 --> 01:04:01.422
What?

820
01:04:01.505 --> 01:04:03.299
Go. You can go. He says "go."

821
01:04:26.530 --> 01:04:27.990
You should speed up.

822
01:04:28.657 --> 01:04:29.658
What? Why?

823
01:04:31.869 --> 01:04:33.037
Katy. go. go. go!

824
01:04:37.041 --> 01:04:38.184
Morris says.

825
01:04:38.208 --> 01:04:40.085
- "Hard right on three."
- What?

826
01:04:40.252 --> 01:04:41.253
Two...

827
01:04:41.337 --> 01:04:42.397
Hard right where?

828
01:04:42.421 --> 01:04:43.797
Now.

829
01:04:51.055 --> 01:04:52.348
And left.

830
01:04:56.769 --> 01:04:58.354
It's all about
staying in the pocket.

831
01:04:58.520 --> 01:05:00.189
- What pocket?
- We're in it now.

832
01:05:00.356 --> 01:05:02.167
What happens if
we don't stay in the pocket?

833
01:05:02.191 --> 01:05:03.192
The forest eats us.

834
01:05:03.359 --> 01:05:04.818
Eats us? What does that mean?

835
01:05:04.985 --> 01:05:06.528
He says it eats us. Go left.

836
01:05:14.745 --> 01:05:16.789
- Watch your back!
- Stay in the pocket.

837
01:05:16.956 --> 01:05:18.540
- How close is it?
- Five meters.

838
01:05:18.707 --> 01:05:20.602
- Stay in the pocket.
- What is that in feet?

839
01:05:20.626 --> 01:05:21.627
Really fricking close.

840
01:05:21.794 --> 01:05:22.795
Stay in the pocket.

841
01:05:22.962 --> 01:05:24.564
Will you just stop saying.
"Stay in the pocket"?

842
01:05:31.095 --> 01:05:33.222
One last right. then
straight on to the end.

843
01:05:41.271 --> 01:05:42.606
You might wanna hurry up.

844
01:05:42.773 --> 01:05:44.608
What do you think I'm doing?

845
01:05:46.235 --> 01:05:47.277
We're not gonna make it.

846
01:05:50.447 --> 01:05:52.032
I'm coming home. Mummy.

847
01:06:04.336 --> 01:06:07.297
Morris says. "Great
job. everyone."

848
01:06:08.716 --> 01:06:11.593
Now. all we have to do is
go through that waterfall.

849
01:06:11.760 --> 01:06:13.554
and we're pretty much there.

850
01:07:03.896 --> 01:07:04.938
Bloody hell.

851
01:07:05.105 --> 01:07:06.857
I think those birds are on fire.

852
01:07:06.940 --> 01:07:09.318
Really? Oh.

853
01:07:09.610 --> 01:07:11.820
Morris says it's normal.

854
01:07:11.987 --> 01:07:14.323
They're old mates of his.

855
01:07:48.232 --> 01:07:50.234
That's a weird horse.

856
01:07:51.652 --> 01:07:53.403
What's it looking at me for?

857
01:08:56.925 --> 01:08:59.052
Hi there!

858
01:08:59.303 --> 01:09:01.221
I am Xu Shang-Chi.

859
01:09:01.847 --> 01:09:04.641
This is my sister. Xu Xialing.

860
01:09:04.808 --> 01:09:07.352
We're Ying Li's children.

861
01:09:11.231 --> 01:09:12.733
This is my friend. Katy.

862
01:09:12.900 --> 01:09:16.528
Get in your car and go home!

863
01:09:16.695 --> 01:09:19.198
Please. You don't understand.

864
01:09:24.286 --> 01:09:25.537
Whoa.

865
01:09:25.621 --> 01:09:27.039
Guang Bo!

866
01:09:28.415 --> 01:09:30.584
What are you doing?

867
01:09:31.210 --> 01:09:33.378
Put down your weapons!

868
01:09:36.340 --> 01:09:38.008
Shang-Chi.

869
01:09:38.467 --> 01:09:39.593
Xialing.

870
01:09:39.760 --> 01:09:43.013
I'm your auntie. Nan.

871
01:09:44.765 --> 01:09:47.476
I've waited so long to meet you.

872
01:09:57.152 --> 01:09:58.779
You look like your mother.

873
01:10:06.620 --> 01:10:07.746
Hi. I'm Katy.

874
01:10:07.955 --> 01:10:09.331
Welcome
to Ta Lo. Katy.

875
01:10:09.414 --> 01:10:10.999
Oh. thank you.

876
01:10:16.797 --> 01:10:19.299
Look who has found
his way home!

877
01:10:19.967 --> 01:10:21.218
I'm not a threat.

878
01:10:21.385 --> 01:10:23.512
Just an entertainer.

879
01:10:23.679 --> 01:10:25.264
Morris can vouch for me.

880
01:10:27.224 --> 01:10:28.600
We don't have much time.

881
01:10:29.059 --> 01:10:30.394
Our father is coming.

882
01:10:38.485 --> 01:10:41.446
Our people have been
here for over 4.000 years.

883
01:10:41.613 --> 01:10:44.408
preparing for something
we hope will never happen.

884
01:10:44.574 --> 01:10:47.119
We are the keepers
of the Dark Gate.

885
01:10:47.286 --> 01:10:49.663
sworn to protect
this realm and yours

886
01:10:49.746 --> 01:10:52.332
from the evil that's
locked behind it.

887
01:10:53.166 --> 01:10:55.377
Our dad is coming
here to open that gate.

888
01:10:55.919 --> 01:10:57.921
He thinks you're
holding our mom there.

889
01:10:59.214 --> 01:11:00.716
Why would he think that?

890
01:11:00.882 --> 01:11:02.092
She told him.

891
01:11:02.259 --> 01:11:04.303
He says he can hear
her asking for help.

892
01:11:06.722 --> 01:11:08.724
Is he wearing the rings?

893
01:11:08.890 --> 01:11:11.018
He hasn't taken
them off since she died.

894
01:11:12.936 --> 01:11:14.563
What do they have
to do with all this?

895
01:11:18.483 --> 01:11:20.569
The realm of Ta
Lo stretches far beyond

896
01:11:20.652 --> 01:11:22.529
the shores of our small village.

897
01:11:22.696 --> 01:11:26.366
We have cities that surpass
any in your universe.

898
01:11:26.533 --> 01:11:29.244
rich with culture and history.

899
01:11:29.411 --> 01:11:31.413
Thousands of years ago.

900
01:11:31.580 --> 01:11:34.833
all of our people lived
in peace and prosperity.

901
01:11:35.917 --> 01:11:39.046
until the attack of the
Dweller-in-Darkness.

902
01:11:39.671 --> 01:11:41.089
He came with his army.

903
01:11:41.173 --> 01:11:44.217
devouring every
soul in their path.

904
01:11:44.384 --> 01:11:48.055
and with each kill.
they grew stronger.

905
01:11:48.722 --> 01:11:51.266
After decimating
our largest cities.

906
01:11:51.433 --> 01:11:54.853
they were headed to your
universe to do the same.

907
01:11:55.020 --> 01:11:58.398
The leaders of Ta Lo sent
their strongest warriors here

908
01:11:58.565 --> 01:12:01.777
to stop them from reaching
the portal to your world.

909
01:12:02.361 --> 01:12:05.489
But our ancestors were
no match for them.

910
01:12:06.615 --> 01:12:09.618
Until The Great Protector

911
01:12:09.743 --> 01:12:13.288
joined their fight
and turned the tide.

912
01:12:13.997 --> 01:12:17.000
Together. they pushed
the Dweller and his army

913
01:12:17.084 --> 01:12:18.293
into the Dark Gate

914
01:12:18.460 --> 01:12:20.921
and locked it behind them.

915
01:12:22.881 --> 01:12:26.301
Our people have guarded
that gate ever since.

916
01:12:26.468 --> 01:12:29.930
empowered by the magic
of The Great Protector

917
01:12:30.097 --> 01:12:32.391
and the gift that she gave us.

918
01:12:44.027 --> 01:12:45.028
Dragon scales.

919
01:12:45.195 --> 01:12:46.863
Makes very good armor.

920
01:12:48.990 --> 01:12:51.034
Your father isn't the
first to come here

921
01:12:51.118 --> 01:12:52.369
to open the Dark Gate.

922
01:12:52.953 --> 01:12:55.205
Many have tried and
failed over the centuries.

923
01:12:55.372 --> 01:12:57.707
and they all had
one thing in common.

924
01:12:57.874 --> 01:12:58.875
They were lured here

925
01:12:58.959 --> 01:13:01.086
by the voice of something
on the other side.

926
01:13:01.878 --> 01:13:04.756
A voice that promised them
their greatest desires.

927
01:13:07.217 --> 01:13:11.388
So you think soul eaters
are talking to our dad?

928
01:13:12.180 --> 01:13:15.517
They know The Ten Rings have
the power to break them free.

929
01:13:19.855 --> 01:13:20.856
Oh.

930
01:13:23.483 --> 01:13:25.068
Here you go.

931
01:13:25.318 --> 01:13:26.319
Oh.

932
01:13:26.862 --> 01:13:28.321
To the range.

933
01:13:29.489 --> 01:13:31.533
What? Okay.

934
01:13:32.284 --> 01:13:34.953
Um. looks like I'm gonna go
deliver some dragon arrows.

935
01:13:35.162 --> 01:13:36.639
Oh. you're gonna deliver
some dragon arrows?

936
01:13:36.663 --> 01:13:38.099
Yeah. Make myself
useful. you know.

937
01:13:38.123 --> 01:13:39.124
Thank you.

938
01:13:41.168 --> 01:13:42.878
Let's go see your mother.

939
01:13:57.559 --> 01:14:00.145
I just love how you guys know
exactly what you wanna do.

940
01:14:00.353 --> 01:14:03.148
and you spend your whole life
getting really good at it.

941
01:14:03.315 --> 01:14:04.900
I wish I was more like that.

942
01:14:05.066 --> 01:14:07.266
It's like every time I get
moderately good at something.

943
01:14:07.319 --> 01:14:09.571
I just quit and
start something new.

944
01:14:09.738 --> 01:14:11.656
But I just know my own limits.

945
01:14:11.823 --> 01:14:14.451
and I'm not gonna waste
my time chasing something

946
01:14:14.534 --> 01:14:16.414
that will ultimately be
a disappointment for me.

947
01:14:16.453 --> 01:14:17.555
That's not me.

948
01:14:17.579 --> 01:14:19.039
Guang Bo.

949
01:14:20.290 --> 01:14:21.625
Let her shoot.

950
01:14:25.003 --> 01:14:28.673
If you aim at nothing.
you hit nothing.

951
01:14:52.155 --> 01:14:54.115
You
were everything to her.

952
01:14:55.450 --> 01:14:57.911
She knew that one day you
would find your way here

953
01:14:58.078 --> 01:15:00.830
and asked me to prepare
something for your arrival.

954
01:15:23.395 --> 01:15:25.313
After losing someone like her.

955
01:15:25.397 --> 01:15:28.024
it's easy to feel
alone in this world.

956
01:15:28.692 --> 01:15:30.360
But you're not.

957
01:15:30.527 --> 01:15:32.779
You are children of this family.

958
01:15:33.363 --> 01:15:35.699
and I welcome you home.

959
01:16:03.351 --> 01:16:05.186
You're not in your
father's house anymore.

960
01:16:06.938 --> 01:16:11.067
In Ta Lo. we train as equals.

961
01:16:12.819 --> 01:16:16.698
You've been in the shadows
long enough. my child.

962
01:16:36.092 --> 01:16:37.492
Guang
Bo. you saw that?

963
01:16:38.053 --> 01:16:39.387
That was tight!

964
01:16:52.776 --> 01:16:54.694
My mother was the only
one who could beat him.

965
01:16:56.279 --> 01:16:58.073
Show me how she did it.

966
01:17:05.330 --> 01:17:06.831
No. sorry.

967
01:17:06.998 --> 01:17:08.583
Sorry. Offside. offside.

968
01:18:09.310 --> 01:18:11.521
Your mother
knew who she was.

969
01:18:12.272 --> 01:18:13.440
Do you?

970
01:19:19.464 --> 01:19:22.509
You are a product of
all who came before you.

971
01:19:23.468 --> 01:19:27.305
The legacy of your family.
the good and the bad.

972
01:19:28.097 --> 01:19:30.433
it is all a part of who you are.

973
01:19:34.813 --> 01:19:36.898
Stop hiding. nephew.

974
01:19:37.732 --> 01:19:39.776
It only prolongs the pain.

975
01:20:12.225 --> 01:20:14.769
We'll be together soon.

976
01:20:21.192 --> 01:20:22.352
Sir.

977
01:20:24.863 --> 01:20:26.364
The men are ready.

978
01:20:27.407 --> 01:20:29.200
The passage will open at dawn.

979
01:20:30.159 --> 01:20:31.786
I'll
prepare the vehicles.

980
01:20:55.935 --> 01:20:57.896
Lead with your breath.

981
01:20:58.354 --> 01:21:01.316
Look into your heart.

982
01:21:01.482 --> 01:21:04.819
the light and the dark.

983
01:21:04.986 --> 01:21:09.073
To know yourself.

984
01:21:09.240 --> 01:21:13.161
you must face them both.

985
01:21:28.259 --> 01:21:30.178
Your husband tried
to destroy us.

986
01:21:30.762 --> 01:21:33.431
The Iron Gang is here
to repay that debt.

987
01:21:34.057 --> 01:21:35.975
My husband is not the
man he used to be.

988
01:21:36.768 --> 01:21:38.144
It doesn't matter.

989
01:21:39.395 --> 01:21:42.649
Your business with him has
nothing to do with my children.

990
01:21:45.568 --> 01:21:47.445
They can go.

991
01:21:47.612 --> 01:21:51.407
but someone has to pay.

992
01:21:56.079 --> 01:21:57.914
Xialing. Shang-Chi.

993
01:21:58.081 --> 01:21:59.082
Go inside.

994
01:21:59.207 --> 01:22:02.001
I'm going to talk to our guests.

995
01:22:08.007 --> 01:22:10.843
But you don't have your powers.

996
01:22:13.554 --> 01:22:15.598
Shang-Chi. you have
nothing to fear.

997
01:23:37.847 --> 01:23:39.057
Mama.

998
01:23:41.684 --> 01:23:42.852
Mama.

999
01:24:01.370 --> 01:24:02.580
Papa.

1000
01:24:11.881 --> 01:24:14.926
She told me I could change.

1001
01:24:16.427 --> 01:24:19.680
That I could leave
my past behind.

1002
01:24:22.100 --> 01:24:24.602
But she was wrong.

1003
01:24:27.814 --> 01:24:30.441
If I hadn't taken them off.

1004
01:24:31.359 --> 01:24:35.321
those men wouldn't
have dared to do this.

1005
01:24:37.782 --> 01:24:40.535
And now they will pay for it.

1006
01:25:34.964 --> 01:25:36.007
Where's your boss?

1007
01:25:36.465 --> 01:25:37.466
I don't know!

1008
01:25:37.884 --> 01:25:39.468
I swear I don't!

1009
01:25:41.053 --> 01:25:42.638
Okay.

1010
01:25:55.985 --> 01:26:00.740
A blood debt has to
be paid by blood.

1011
01:26:01.574 --> 01:26:03.367
Will you help me?

1012
01:26:33.314 --> 01:26:34.523
We found the man

1013
01:26:34.607 --> 01:26:36.692
responsible for
killing your mother.

1014
01:26:37.902 --> 01:26:40.988
It is your right to finish
this for both of us.

1015
01:26:42.114 --> 01:26:43.741
And when you return.

1016
01:26:43.908 --> 01:26:47.411
we will rebuild The Ten
Rings to what it once was.

1017
01:27:08.933 --> 01:27:10.559
Been looking everywhere for ya.

1018
01:27:18.484 --> 01:27:19.694
You okay?

1019
01:27:24.073 --> 01:27:27.451
I'm not who you think I am.

1020
01:27:27.618 --> 01:27:29.453
You already apologized
for that. We're good...

1021
01:27:29.620 --> 01:27:31.580
That's not what
I'm talking about.

1022
01:27:33.874 --> 01:27:35.084
Okay.

1023
01:27:36.669 --> 01:27:38.462
What... What is it?

1024
01:27:44.051 --> 01:27:48.889
When my dad sent me to find
the man who killed my mom...

1025
01:27:51.600 --> 01:27:53.811
I told you I couldn't
go through with it.

1026
01:27:58.858 --> 01:28:00.359
I lied.

1027
01:28:04.613 --> 01:28:06.907
I thought that I
could change my name.

1028
01:28:07.074 --> 01:28:09.994
start a new life. pretend
like it never happened.

1029
01:28:10.161 --> 01:28:11.370
But...

1030
01:28:18.294 --> 01:28:20.546
She would hate the
person I've become.

1031
01:28:27.261 --> 01:28:29.472
Your dad trained you
to be an assassin

1032
01:28:29.555 --> 01:28:31.474
when you were seven.

1033
01:28:32.224 --> 01:28:35.811
He sent you on a hit at 14.

1034
01:28:37.772 --> 01:28:40.149
You realize how messed
up that is. right?

1035
01:28:43.778 --> 01:28:46.280
My mom is dead because of him.

1036
01:28:49.241 --> 01:28:51.994
And now he's coming
to destroy her home.

1037
01:29:01.379 --> 01:29:04.632
A blood debt has to
be paid by blood.

1038
01:29:07.551 --> 01:29:09.303
What
are you saying?

1039
01:29:12.848 --> 01:29:15.059
I'm gonna do what
he trained me to do.

1040
01:29:21.065 --> 01:29:22.608
I'm gonna kill him.

1041
01:30:10.072 --> 01:30:11.073
He's here.

1042
01:30:23.419 --> 01:30:24.420
No!

1043
01:30:24.503 --> 01:30:25.754
You're not ready.

1044
01:30:25.921 --> 01:30:27.965
She stays here.

1045
01:31:21.685 --> 01:31:23.330
Are you
here to help the people

1046
01:31:23.354 --> 01:31:25.814
holding your own mother captive?

1047
01:31:26.232 --> 01:31:27.816
She
isn't back there.

1048
01:31:28.192 --> 01:31:29.193
You're being lied to

1049
01:31:29.276 --> 01:31:31.445
by a creature who wants
to destroy us all.

1050
01:31:32.905 --> 01:31:34.990
Is that what they told you?

1051
01:31:35.574 --> 01:31:38.202
I know my wife's voice.

1052
01:31:38.410 --> 01:31:40.955
I miss my sister
as much as you do.

1053
01:31:41.121 --> 01:31:43.707
but this is not the way
to honor her memory.

1054
01:31:43.874 --> 01:31:45.668
Did you honor her when
you turned her away

1055
01:31:45.751 --> 01:31:46.752
from your gate?

1056
01:31:46.877 --> 01:31:49.380
You fool. We turned you away.

1057
01:31:49.547 --> 01:31:52.091
The sins of your past would
have destroyed this place.

1058
01:31:52.424 --> 01:31:56.720
Be careful how you
speak to me. young man.

1059
01:31:57.137 --> 01:32:00.933
I've lived ten of
your lifetimes.

1060
01:32:02.476 --> 01:32:04.103
Let me pass.

1061
01:32:04.436 --> 01:32:06.480
We cannot do that.

1062
01:32:25.457 --> 01:32:26.625
Burn it down.

1063
01:33:30.564 --> 01:33:31.690
Stop him!

1064
01:34:07.309 --> 01:34:10.312
Are you planning to
stop me all by yourself?

1065
01:34:14.650 --> 01:34:16.068
I'm not afraid of you.

1066
01:34:23.367 --> 01:34:24.576
Yes. you are.

1067
01:34:30.207 --> 01:34:33.627
You've spent your
entire life afraid.

1068
01:34:33.794 --> 01:34:35.838
Always running.

1069
01:34:36.004 --> 01:34:37.297
always hiding.

1070
01:34:52.521 --> 01:34:54.690
You were there when
they came for her.

1071
01:34:54.857 --> 01:34:57.025
and you did nothing.

1072
01:34:57.609 --> 01:35:00.487
You stood at a window
and watched her die!

1073
01:35:35.314 --> 01:35:37.024
She was gone and we needed you.

1074
01:35:38.233 --> 01:35:41.445
But you chose those damn
rings over us.

1075
01:35:45.532 --> 01:35:47.034
You trained your
son to be a killer.

1076
01:35:48.243 --> 01:35:49.369
Is this what you wanted?

1077
01:36:06.762 --> 01:36:08.430
Even if you could
bring her back.

1078
01:36:10.224 --> 01:36:12.851
what makes you think she'd
want anything to do with you?

1079
01:36:38.460 --> 01:36:40.170
Save me.

1080
01:36:41.171 --> 01:36:43.507
Save me. my dear.

1081
01:37:03.318 --> 01:37:05.195
Save me.

1082
01:37:05.654 --> 01:37:08.073
I'm coming. my love.

1083
01:37:49.656 --> 01:37:50.976
He
breached the gate!

1084
01:37:55.329 --> 01:37:56.598
Those things are
gonna kill us all

1085
01:37:56.622 --> 01:37:58.206
if we don't work together.

1086
01:37:58.373 --> 01:38:00.417
You think I'm going
to fall for that?

1087
01:38:00.584 --> 01:38:02.753
Your weapons are
useless against them.

1088
01:38:03.211 --> 01:38:04.838
We don't need your help.

1089
01:38:05.380 --> 01:38:07.633
We are the mighty Ten Rings.

1090
01:38:07.716 --> 01:38:09.134
and any...

1091
01:38:33.825 --> 01:38:36.411
We... We should work together.

1092
01:38:36.578 --> 01:38:38.622
Release them.

1093
01:38:38.789 --> 01:38:40.540
Release them!

1094
01:38:46.296 --> 01:38:47.589
What are they doing?

1095
01:38:47.756 --> 01:38:50.217
Stealing souls to
feed the Dweller-in-Darkness.

1096
01:38:50.342 --> 01:38:51.718
If it grows strong enough.

1097
01:38:51.802 --> 01:38:53.242
it will break right
through the gate.

1098
01:38:53.387 --> 01:38:55.347
That was just the beginning.

1099
01:38:58.266 --> 01:38:59.559
It's too dangerous.

1100
01:38:59.726 --> 01:39:01.246
I have
to help my friends.

1101
01:39:05.273 --> 01:39:07.275
Don't die.

1102
01:39:08.360 --> 01:39:11.113
Everyone to the water now!

1103
01:39:11.196 --> 01:39:12.465
To the lake! Let's go!

1104
01:39:12.489 --> 01:39:13.699
Let's go!

1105
01:39:15.826 --> 01:39:17.869
Hey. where's your brother?

1106
01:39:18.036 --> 01:39:19.746
I was hoping you knew.

1107
01:39:27.629 --> 01:39:28.630
Save me.

1108
01:39:53.196 --> 01:39:56.116
Aim at the sky. to win or die!

1109
01:40:09.880 --> 01:40:11.631
Deep breath.

1110
01:40:27.314 --> 01:40:29.775
Shang-Chi. you have
nothing to fear.

1111
01:40:30.942 --> 01:40:33.111
You have the heart
of our dragon.

1112
01:40:33.904 --> 01:40:37.240
I will always be a part of
you. And your dad will too.

1113
01:40:37.866 --> 01:40:41.995
Take everything we've given
you and make it your own.

1114
01:40:59.262 --> 01:41:01.515
I'm so proud of you.

1115
01:41:05.852 --> 01:41:08.271
Our family needs you.

1116
01:41:09.689 --> 01:41:10.690
Go.

1117
01:42:04.828 --> 01:42:06.580
Draw.

1118
01:42:10.542 --> 01:42:11.877
Fire!

1119
01:42:39.279 --> 01:42:41.198
You have
to stop your father!

1120
01:43:12.312 --> 01:43:14.439
She's not back there. Dad.

1121
01:43:15.899 --> 01:43:19.736
Get out of my way. boy.

1122
01:43:20.987 --> 01:43:21.988
No.

1123
01:44:25.802 --> 01:44:27.053
Calm down. mate.

1124
01:44:27.220 --> 01:44:28.700
I'm not dead. it's
just a performance.

1125
01:44:28.847 --> 01:44:30.473
Now get down here
and play along.

1126
01:47:13.845 --> 01:47:15.597
I have to save her.

1127
01:47:17.307 --> 01:47:19.184
She's calling to me.

1128
01:47:22.687 --> 01:47:24.272
I wish that were true.

1129
01:47:27.400 --> 01:47:28.776
Dad. please.

1130
01:47:31.321 --> 01:47:33.031
Your family needs you.

1131
01:47:42.165 --> 01:47:43.917
Let me out!

1132
01:48:14.531 --> 01:48:15.615
Shit.

1133
01:49:58.217 --> 01:49:59.510
It's headed for the village!

1134
01:51:49.454 --> 01:51:53.791
If it gets our dragon's
soul. it will be unstoppable!

1135
01:51:56.836 --> 01:51:58.337
Aim for the throat!

1136
01:52:46.677 --> 01:52:48.471
You have to let me go.

1137
01:52:55.728 --> 01:52:57.271
Let go!

1138
01:52:59.190 --> 01:53:00.942
I'm not
leaving you again.

1139
01:53:19.210 --> 01:53:20.503
Holy shit.

1140
01:53:52.660 --> 01:53:54.537
Go.

1141
01:56:02.581 --> 01:56:03.767
<i>Tonight.</i>

1142
01:56:03.791 --> 01:56:05.543
<i>we honor those who
gave their lives</i>

1143
01:56:05.626 --> 01:56:07.420
so we might see another day.

1144
01:56:08.963 --> 01:56:10.631
They were more than warriors.

1145
01:56:11.757 --> 01:56:15.177
They were our
mothers and fathers.

1146
01:56:15.344 --> 01:56:18.055
our sisters and brothers.

1147
01:56:19.223 --> 01:56:22.560
And though we will always
hold on to their memories.

1148
01:56:24.186 --> 01:56:28.733
tonight we release them to
rest with our ancestors.

1149
01:56:35.573 --> 01:56:37.366
Farewell. Dad.

1150
01:56:38.242 --> 01:56:39.869
Mom. we'll be okay.

1151
01:56:42.246 --> 01:56:44.040
A thousand years ago.

1152
01:56:44.498 --> 01:56:46.834
and a thousand years from now.

1153
01:56:47.585 --> 01:56:50.421
we will always be together.

1154
01:57:32.797 --> 01:57:34.608
<i>I seriously thought
we were going to die.</i>

1155
01:57:34.632 --> 01:57:36.068
And I'd only learned
how to shoot a bow.

1156
01:57:36.092 --> 01:57:37.343
like. a day earlier.

1157
01:57:37.510 --> 01:57:38.636
now I'm on a battlefield.

1158
01:57:38.719 --> 01:57:41.013
killing all these Soul
Suckers with Shaun's auntie.

1159
01:57:41.180 --> 01:57:43.390
who's this awesome.
magical kung fu goddess.

1160
01:57:43.557 --> 01:57:45.035
And I'm hanging on to
The Great Protector

1161
01:57:45.059 --> 01:57:46.119
with my sister at this point.

1162
01:57:46.143 --> 01:57:48.145
trying not to get eaten
by the Mega Soul Sucker.

1163
01:57:48.312 --> 01:57:50.606
Oh. the Mega Soul Sucker
was such a nasty bitch.

1164
01:57:50.773 --> 01:57:52.334
Yeah. It was trying
to eat our dragon's soul.

1165
01:57:52.358 --> 01:57:53.418
Which would
have allowed it

1166
01:57:53.442 --> 01:57:54.544
to destroy the entire universe.

1167
01:57:54.568 --> 01:57:55.569
Yeah.

1168
01:57:55.653 --> 01:57:56.880
I only had
one arrow left.

1169
01:57:56.904 --> 01:57:58.781
and all I could hear
in the back of my mind

1170
01:57:58.948 --> 01:58:00.407
was my mom's voice saying.

1171
01:58:00.574 --> 01:58:02.785
"Just take the shot.
you little mooch!"

1172
01:58:02.952 --> 01:58:05.454
And so. I aimed right
for the Sucker's throat

1173
01:58:05.538 --> 01:58:07.456
- and I let her fly.
- She hit it dead on.

1174
01:58:07.790 --> 01:58:09.125
And then Shaun
used the Ten Rings

1175
01:58:09.208 --> 01:58:11.877
to do this crazy
Kamehameha fireball

1176
01:58:11.961 --> 01:58:13.561
that exploded the thing...

1177
01:58:13.587 --> 01:58:15.506
and he saved the world.

1178
01:58:16.841 --> 01:58:19.677
Yeah. we. uh. lost some
good people that day...

1179
01:58:21.846 --> 01:58:23.180
but we made it.

1180
01:58:23.681 --> 01:58:25.057
We made it.

1181
01:58:26.767 --> 01:58:28.227
Are you done mocking me?

1182
01:58:28.435 --> 01:58:30.271
Oh. no. We're not mocking you.

1183
01:58:30.437 --> 01:58:31.814
So where is this
sister of yours?

1184
01:58:31.981 --> 01:58:33.899
She's back at my dad's compound.

1185
01:58:33.983 --> 01:58:35.151
shutting down his operations.

1186
01:58:35.317 --> 01:58:36.962
Yeah. his dad was the
head of The Ten Rings

1187
01:58:36.986 --> 01:58:38.487
for the past thousand years.

1188
01:58:40.030 --> 01:58:42.074
Two weeks ago. you were
parking cars for tips.

1189
01:58:42.241 --> 01:58:44.535
and you want me to believe
you're now saving the world

1190
01:58:44.702 --> 01:58:46.495
from soul-sucking monsters?

1191
01:58:47.163 --> 01:58:48.473
I know. you're
trying to get me back

1192
01:58:48.497 --> 01:58:50.225
for what I said last time.
but I'm not gonna apologize...

1193
01:58:51.333 --> 01:58:52.811
for speaking the
truth as a friend.

1194
01:58:52.835 --> 01:58:55.462
I really meant what I said.
and. in fact. I actually think

1195
01:58:55.629 --> 01:58:57.965
this whole bit you're doing
just further proves my point.

1196
01:58:58.132 --> 01:58:59.258
You guys are obviously...

1197
01:59:00.551 --> 01:59:02.178
- What?
- Shang-Chi.

1198
01:59:04.930 --> 01:59:06.223
Shang-Chi.

1199
01:59:07.308 --> 01:59:08.851
Uh... Here.

1200
01:59:09.018 --> 01:59:10.019
Present.

1201
01:59:13.731 --> 01:59:14.857
My name is Wong.

1202
01:59:16.108 --> 01:59:18.277
Yeah. I know. sir.
I'm a huge fan...

1203
01:59:18.444 --> 01:59:19.904
Do you have the rings?

1204
01:59:21.405 --> 01:59:22.865
Uh... Yeah. yes.

1205
01:59:23.032 --> 01:59:25.993
Good. Let's go. we have
a lot to talk about.

1206
01:59:26.493 --> 01:59:27.578
You too.

1207
01:59:30.372 --> 01:59:31.373
Me too?

1208
01:59:34.585 --> 01:59:36.545
- I think we should...
- Yeah.

1209
01:59:36.629 --> 01:59:38.923
- Uh. we
gotta go. - Yeah.

1210
01:59:40.216 --> 01:59:43.636
I know this is. like. crazy.
but I'm gonna text you.

1211
01:59:43.802 --> 01:59:46.680
and we'll do this again.
Nice to see you. John.

1212
01:59:46.847 --> 01:59:48.724
I'll Venmo you for the...

1213
02:02:00.105 --> 02:02:01.315
Hmm.

1214
02:02:02.691 --> 02:02:05.819
They don't match any
artifacts from our codex.

1215
02:02:07.196 --> 02:02:08.614
What do you think?

1216
02:02:08.697 --> 02:02:10.574
Mm. I'm not sure.

1217
02:02:12.868 --> 02:02:15.996
They're not
vibranium. Chitauri?

1218
02:02:17.414 --> 02:02:19.833
Not like any alien
tech I've seen.

1219
02:02:20.834 --> 02:02:22.020
How long did your dad have them

1220
02:02:22.044 --> 02:02:23.545
before he gave them to you?

1221
02:02:24.755 --> 02:02:26.048
Um...

1222
02:02:26.131 --> 02:02:27.716
About a thousand years.

1223
02:02:28.008 --> 02:02:29.718
Their thermoluminescence
indicates

1224
02:02:29.802 --> 02:02:31.136
they're older than that.

1225
02:02:31.345 --> 02:02:32.930
By a lot.

1226
02:02:33.180 --> 02:02:35.432
The first time you
used the rings.

1227
02:02:35.808 --> 02:02:38.227
we felt it in Kamar-Taj.

1228
02:02:46.944 --> 02:02:48.404
What is it?

1229
02:02:48.529 --> 02:02:49.988
A beacon.

1230
02:02:50.155 --> 02:02:52.074
They're
sending a message.

1231
02:02:53.784 --> 02:02:55.828
A message to where?

1232
02:02:58.372 --> 02:03:00.374
I'm so sorry. I have
to deal with this.

1233
02:03:00.582 --> 02:03:01.726
You can get my
number from Bruce.

1234
02:03:01.750 --> 02:03:03.168
It was so nice to meet you.

1235
02:03:04.962 --> 02:03:07.381
Yeah. I... I don't
have her number.

1236
02:03:07.798 --> 02:03:09.967
She... She does this a lot.

1237
02:03:10.717 --> 02:03:12.928
Guys. stay safe.

1238
02:03:13.887 --> 02:03:16.140
Welcome to the circus.

1239
02:03:22.813 --> 02:03:25.357
I know this is a lot to take in.

1240
02:03:25.524 --> 02:03:27.985
but you're gonna have to
start getting used to that.

1241
02:03:28.485 --> 02:03:31.530
From now on. the
trajectory of your lives

1242
02:03:31.697 --> 02:03:34.783
will be like nothing you've
ever experienced before.

1243
02:03:35.617 --> 02:03:37.619
And there's no going back.

1244
02:03:39.538 --> 02:03:41.707
You both have a long
journey ahead of you.

1245
02:03:42.499 --> 02:03:45.127
Go home. get some rest.

1246
02:03:47.171 --> 02:03:48.547
Yeah. That's a good idea.

1247
02:03:48.630 --> 02:03:51.675
Yeah. Yeah. we probably
should do that.

1248
02:03:53.177 --> 02:03:54.553
Or...

1249
02:03:57.097 --> 02:04:00.142
<i>Welcome
to the Hotel California</i>

1250
02:04:01.977 --> 02:04:05.105
<i>-Such a lovely place
-Such a lovely place</i>

1251
02:04:05.272 --> 02:04:08.817
<i>-Such a lovely face
-Such a lovely face</i>

1252
02:04:10.444 --> 02:04:12.863
<i>Plenty of room at
the Hotel California</i>

1253
02:04:15.449 --> 02:04:18.535
<i>-Any time of year
-Any time of year</i>

1254
02:04:18.702 --> 02:04:20.078
<i>You can find it here</i>

1255
02:04:22.164 --> 02:04:24.625
<i>Her mind is Tiffany-twisted</i>

1256
02:04:25.375 --> 02:04:28.378
<i>She got the Mercedes bends. uh</i>

1257
02:04:28.712 --> 02:04:34.426
<i>She got a lot of pretty.
pretty boys she calls friends</i>

1258
02:04:35.761 --> 02:04:40.849
<i>How they dance in the
courtyard. sweet summer sweat</i>

1259
02:04:41.892 --> 02:04:47.898
<i>Some dance to remember.
some dance to forget</i>

1260
02:04:48.524 --> 02:04:54.112
<i>So I called up the Captain
"Please bring me my wine"</i>

1261
02:04:54.238 --> 02:05:00.827
<i>He said. "We haven't had
that spirit here since 1969"</i>

1262
02:05:01.537 --> 02:05:07.459
<i>And still those voices
are calling from far away</i>

1263
02:05:08.335 --> 02:05:10.671
<i>Wake you up in the
middle of the night</i>

1264
02:05:11.296 --> 02:05:14.007
<i>Just to hear them say</i>

1265
02:05:14.800 --> 02:05:18.637
<i>Welcome to the Hotel California</i>

1266
02:05:20.430 --> 02:05:23.559
<i>-Such a lovely place
-Such a lovely place</i>

1267
02:05:23.642 --> 02:05:26.103
<i>Such a lovely face</i>

1268
02:05:26.937 --> 02:05:31.441
<i>They livin' it up at
the Hotel California</i>

1269
02:05:33.277 --> 02:05:36.446
<i>-What a nice surprise
-What a nice surprise</i>

1270
02:05:36.572 --> 02:05:39.449
<i>Bring your alibis</i>

1271
02:10:59.227 --> 02:11:00.520
They're waiting.

1272
02:11:27.881 --> 02:11:29.090
Let's get started.

1273
02:11:29.257 --> 02:11:30.759
We have a lot of work to do.

